  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Purpose of the study is to investigate and quantify known and possible new riskfactors for
      nosocomiel infection and death in the intensive care setting.

      As new riskfactors Mannose Binding Lechtin and Procalcitonin are chosen and compared to
      established riskfactors.
    </textblock>
